abstract: BARCELONA — Investors, analysts and cellphone executives on Monday cheered Vodafone's $11.1 billion acquisition of a controlling stake in the Indian mobile phone company Hutchison Essar, a move that marks a change in direction and a jump into the unknown for British company.
lead_paragraph: BARCELONA — Investors, analysts and cellphone executives on Monday cheered Vodafone's $11.1 billion acquisition of a controlling stake in the Indian mobile phone company Hutchison Essar, a move that marks a change in direction and a jump into the unknown for British company.
headline_main: India deal puts Vodafone in new world - Business - International Herald Tribune

abstract: After going 4-19 the past two seasons, Illinois has left the tight-knit world of college football abuzz by putting together one of the nation’s best recruiting classes.
snippet: After going 4-19 the past two seasons, Illinois has left the tight-knit world of college football abuzz by putting together one of the nation’s best recruiting classes.
lead_paragraph: Illinois, one of the worst teams among the major conferences in college football in recent seasons, has astounded experts and enraged rivals by putting together one of the nation’s best recruiting classes.
